{{信息安全}}
'''勒索軟體'''，又稱'''勒索病毒'''，是一種特殊的[[惡意軟體|惡意軟體]]，又被人歸類為「阻斷存取式攻擊」（denial-of-access attack），其與其他病毒最大的不同在於手法以及中毒方式。其中一种勒索軟體仅是單純地將受害者的電腦锁起来，而另一種則系統性地[[加密|加密]]受害者硬碟上的檔案。所有的勒索軟體都會要求受害者繳納贖金以取回對電腦的控制權，或是取回受害者根本無從自行取得的解密金鑰以便解密档案。勒索軟體通常透過[[木馬病毒|木馬病毒]]的形式傳播，將自身為掩蓋為看似無害的檔案，通常会通过假冒成普通的电子邮件等[[社会工程学|社会工程学]]方法欺骗受害者点击链接下载，但也有可能与许多其他[[蠕虫病毒|蠕虫病毒]]一样利用软件的漏洞在联网的电脑间传播。<ref name="academia.edu">[https://www.academia.edu/24409160/5_Steps_to_Take_on_Ransomware_A_Defense-in-Layers_Approach Musa, S. (2016). 5 Steps to Take on Ransomware.]</ref>

原先勒索病毒只在[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]境內盛行，但隨著時間推進，受害者開始廣布全球。<ref name="tw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|title=Ransom Trojans spreading beyond Russian heartland|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702211354/http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="FBI">{{Cite web|url=http://www.fbi.gov/news/stories/2012/august/new-internet-scam/new-internet-scam|title=New Internet scam: Ransomware...|date=2012-08-09|publisher=FBI|accessdate=2016-05-23|archive-date=2012-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121017221218/http://www.fbi.gov/news/stories/2012/august/new-internet-scam/new-internet-scam|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="IC3">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ic3.gov/media/2012/121130.aspx|title=Citadel malware continues to deliver Reveton ransomware...|date=2012-11-30|publisher=Internet Crime Complaint Center (IC3)|accessdate=2016-05-23|archive-date=2017-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304011822/https://www.ic3.gov/media/2012/121130.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年6月，網路安全公司[[Intel_Security|McAfee]]釋出了一份數據，顯示該公司光在該年度（2013）第一季就取得了超過250,000種不同的勒索病毒樣本，並表示該數字是去年（2012）同季的超過兩倍。 <ref name="infoworld-mcafeeransom">{{Cite web|url=http://www.infoworld.com/t/security/mcafee-cyber-criminals-using-android-malware-and-ransomware-the-most-219916|title=Update: McAfee: Cyber criminals using Android malware and ransomware the most|accessdate=2013-09-16|work=InfoWorld|archive-date=2014-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702193605/http://www.infoworld.com/t/security/mcafee-cyber-criminals-using-android-malware-and-ransomware-the-most-219916|dead-url=no}}</ref> 隨著[[CryptoLocker|CryptoLocker]]的流行，加密形式的勒索軟體開始進行大規模的攻擊，在遭當局瓦解以前取得了估計三百萬[[美金|美元]]的贖金。<ref name="cl-takedown">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-28661463|title=Cryptolocker victims to get files back for free|date=2014-08-06|accessdate=2014-08-18|agency=BBC News|archive-date=2014-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140809134435/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-28661463|dead-url=no}}</ref> 另一個勒索軟體CryptoWall，被美國[[聯邦調查局|聯邦調查局]]估計在2015年6月以前獲得了超過一百八十萬美元的贖金。<ref name="ars-fbicryptowall">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/06/fbi-says-crypto-ransomware-has-raked-in-18-million-for-cybercriminals/|title=FBI says crypto ransomware has raked in >$18 million for cybercriminals|accessdate=2015-06-25|website=Ars Technica|archive-date=2016-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161023030108/http://arstechnica.com/security/2015/06/fbi-says-crypto-ransomware-has-raked-in-18-million-for-cybercriminals/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 行為 ==
勒索軟體通常透過[[木馬病毒|木馬病毒]]的方式傳播，例如透過下載檔案夾帶，或是透過網路系統的漏洞而進入受害者的電腦。勒索軟體在進入後，會直接執行，或是透過網路下載病毒的[[有效负载|實體數據]]，並[[恐嚇軟體|恐嚇]]受害者。恐嚇訊息隨著不同的病毒而異，例如假借執法機關的名義，恐嚇受害者的電腦被發現進行非法行動，如[[色情|色情]]、[[盗版|盜版媒體]]，或是非法的作業系統等。<ref name="cw-ranactivate">{{Cite web|url=http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9215711/Ransomware_squeezes_users_with_bogus_Windows_activation_demand|title=Ransomware squeezes users with bogus Windows activation demand|accessdate=2012-03-09|publisher=Computerworld|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703000708/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9215711/Ransomware_squeezes_users_with_bogus_Windows_activation_demand|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hsfi-ransom">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hs.fi/english/article/Police+warn+of+extortion+messages+sent+in+their+name/1329103586716|title=Police warn of extortion messages sent in their name|accessdate=2012-03-09|publisher=[[Helsingin_Sanomat|Helsingin Sanomat]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314102017/http://www.hs.fi/english/article/Police+warn+of+extortion+messages+sent+in+their+name/1329103586716|archivedate=2012-03-14}}</ref><ref name="pcw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/204577/alleged_ransomware_gang_investigated_by_moscow_police.html|title=Alleged Ransomware Gang Investigated by Moscow Police|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=McMillian|first=Robert|publisher=PC World|archive-date=2011-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111225232509/http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/204577/alleged_ransomware_gang_investigated_by_moscow_police.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

某些實體數據只將作業系統鎖住，直到受害者付清贖金後才將電腦解鎖。實體數據可能以數種手段來達成恐嚇，包括將[[Windows|Windows]]的[[使用者介面|使用者介面]]（Windows Shell）綁定為病毒程式，<ref name="kaspersky-german">{{Cite web|url=http://www.securelist.com/en/blog/6155/Ransomware_Fake_Federal_German_Police_BKA_notice|title=Ransomware: Fake Federal German Police (BKA) notice|accessdate=2012-03-10|publisher=SecureList (Kaspersky Lab)|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120205194457/http://www.securelist.com/en/blog/6155/Ransomware_Fake_Federal_German_Police_BKA_notice|archivedate=2012-02-05|df=}}</ref> 或甚至修改磁碟的[[主啟動磁區|主啟動磁區]]、硬碟分割表等。 <ref name="kaspersky-mbr">{{Cite web|url=http://www.securelist.com/en/blog/208188032/And_Now_an_MBR_Ransomware|title=And Now, an MBR Ransomware|accessdate=2012-03-10|publisher=SecureList (Kaspersky Lab)|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120414234314/http://www.securelist.com/en/blog/208188032/And_Now_an_MBR_Ransomware|archivedate=2012-04-14|df=}}</ref> 最嚴重的一種實體數據將受害者的檔案[[加密|加密]]，以多種加密方法讓受害者無法使用檔案，唯一的方法通常就是向該病毒的作者繳納贖金，換取加密金鑰，以解開加密檔案。<ref name="young">{{Cite conference|last1=Young|first1=A.|last2=M. Yung|doi=10.1109/SECPRI.1996.502676|title=Cryptovirology: extortion-based security threats and countermeasures|pages=129–140|conference=IEEE Symposium on Security and Privacy|year=1996|isbn=0-8186-7417-2|pmid=|pmc=}}</ref><ref name="young-2">{{Cite news|title=Building a Cryptovirus Using Microsoft's Cryptographic API|publisher=[[Springer-Verlag|Springer-Verlag]]|year=2005|editor-last=Zhou|editor-first=Jianying|pages=389–401|author=Adam Young|journal=Information Security: 8th International Conference, ISC 2005|editor2-first=Javier|editor2-last=Lopez}}</ref><ref name="young-3">{{Cite journal|title=Cryptoviral Extortion Using Microsoft's Crypto API: Can Crypto APIs Help the Enemy?|last=Young|first=Adam|journal=International Journal of Information Security|publisher=[[Springer-Verlag|Springer-Verlag]]|issue=2|doi=10.1007/s10207-006-0082-7|year=2006|volume=5|pages=67–76}}</ref>

獲得贖金是這類病毒的最終目標。要讓病毒的開發者不易被執法單位發現，匿名的繳款管道是開發者的必要元素。有數種的管道發現被開發者用作匿名繳款，例如匯款、簡訊小額付款<ref name="zdnet">{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.zdnet.com/security/?p=3197|title=New ransomware locks PCs, demands premium SMS for removal|accessdate=2009-05-02|date=2009-04-22|last=Danchev|first=Dancho|publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]]|archive-date=2009-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090426055732/http://blogs.zdnet.com/security/?p=3197|dead-url=no}}</ref>、線上虛擬貨幣（Ukash、Paysafecard）<ref name="tw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|title=Ransom Trojans spreading beyond Russian heartland|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702211354/http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="cw-pirated">{{Cite web|url=http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9219745/Ransomware_plays_pirated_Windows_card_demands_143|title=Ransomware plays pirated Windows card, demands $143|accessdate=2012-03-09|publisher=Computerworld|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703021642/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9219745/Ransomware_plays_pirated_Windows_card_demands_143|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="arstechnica">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/news/2007/07/new-trojans-give-us-300-or-the-data-gets-it.ars|title=New Trojans: give us $300, or the data gets it!|accessdate=2009-04-16|date=2007-07-18|last=Cheng|first=Jacqui|publisher=Ars Technica|archive-date=2011-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110912140908/http://arstechnica.com/security/news/2007/07/new-trojans-give-us-300-or-the-data-gets-it.ars|dead-url=no}}</ref>、數位貨幣[[比特币|比特幣]]等。<ref name="ars-cryptolocker">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/security/2013/10/youre-infected-if-you-want-to-see-your-data-again-pay-us-300-in-bitcoins/|title=You’re infected—if you want to see your data again, pay us $300 in Bitcoins|accessdate=2013-10-23|work=Ars Technica|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110004940/http://arstechnica.com/security/2013/10/youre-infected-if-you-want-to-see-your-data-again-pay-us-300-in-bitcoins/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="computerworld-cryptodefense">{{Cite web|url=http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9247348/CryptoDefense_ransomware_leaves_decryption_key_accessible|title=CryptoDefense ransomware leaves decryption key accessible|accessdate=2014-04-07|work=Computerworld|publisher=IDG|archive-date=2014-07-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703000139/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9247348/CryptoDefense_ransomware_leaves_decryption_key_accessible|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tm-cryptodefense">{{Cite web|url=https://www.techiemotto.com/ransomware-attacks-windows-computer/75/|title=What to do if Ransomware Attacks on your Windows Computer?|accessdate=2016-04-25|work=Techie Motto|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160523092754/https://www.techiemotto.com/ransomware-attacks-windows-computer/75/|archivedate=2016-05-23}}</ref>

== 歷史 ==

=== 加密性勒索軟體 ===
最早已知的此種病毒是1989年的"AIDS" Trojan病毒，由Joseph Popp製作。該病毒的實體數據會宣稱受害者的某個軟體已經結束了授權使用，並且加密磁碟上的檔案，要求繳出189美元的費用給''PC Cyborg Corporation''以解除鎖定。開發者Popp在法庭上以[[精神障碍辩护|精神障礙（無行為能力）]]為自己辯護，但他仍承諾將獲得的非法款項用於資助[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]的研究。<ref name="tr-extortion">{{Cite web|url=http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/security/ransomware-extortion-via-the-internet/2976|title=Ransomware: Extortion via the Internet|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Kassner|first=Michael|publisher=TechRepublic|archive-date=2012-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120621032113/http://www.techrepublic.com/blog/security/ransomware-extortion-via-the-internet/2976|dead-url=no}}</ref> 使用公開金鑰加密的構想是1996年由Adam L. Young和Moti Yung所提出的。兩人指出，AIDS Trojan之所以無法有效發揮作用，是因為其採用的是[[對稱密鑰加密|私鑰加密]]，該技術的加密金鑰會儲存於病毒的原始碼中，從而瓦解該病毒的作用。兩人並且實作了一隻[[概念验证|概念驗證]]的實驗性病毒，在Macintosh SE/30電腦上使用[[RSA加密演算法|RSA]]及[[微型加密算法|TEA]]演算法加密資料。他們將這種行為稱作明顯的「加密病毒勒索」（''cryptoviral extortion''），屬於現今稱作[[加密病毒學|加密病毒學]]中的一個分支。<ref name="young">{{Cite conference|last1=Young|first1=A.|last2=M. Yung|doi=10.1109/SECPRI.1996.502676|title=Cryptovirology: extortion-based security threats and countermeasures|pages=129–140|conference=IEEE Symposium on Security and Privacy|year=1996|isbn=0-8186-7417-2|pmid=|pmc=}}</ref> 兩人在1996年的[[IEEE|IEEE]]安全與隱私研討會（IEEE S&P）中描述了攻擊者利用電子貨幣從被害者身上勒贖的過程：「專門的加密病毒能被設計成搜尋受害者的電子貨幣並加密。這樣一來，攻擊者就能名正言順的保證受害者付錢，否則受害者將失去所有的電子貨幣。」
<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="73"></span>

2005年5月開始，勒索軟體變得更為猖獗。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.networkworld.com/buzz/2005/092605-ransom.html?page=3|title=Files for ransom|accessdate=2009-04-17|date=2005-09-26|last=Schaibly|first=Susan|publisher=[[Network_World|Network World]]|archive-date=2013-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019123609/http://www.networkworld.com/buzz/2005/092605-ransom.html?page=3|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在2006年中，勒索軟體開始運用更加複雜的RSA加密手段，甚至加長金鑰的長度，像是Gpcode、TROJ.RANSOM.A、Archiveus、Krotten、Cryzip、MayArchive等病毒。例如在2006年6月發現的Gpcode.AG使用了660位元的RSA公鑰。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://theregister.co.uk/2006/07/24/ransomware/|title=Ransomware getting harder to break|accessdate=2009-04-18|date=2006-07-24|last=Leyden|first=John|publisher=The Register|archive-date=2016-12-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207194401/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2006/07/24/ransomware//|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2008年6月，發現了該病毒的新變種Gpcode.AK。該變種使用了1024位元的RSA公鑰，據信在不使用[[分散式計算|分散式計算]]的情況下，破解該金鑰對單一電腦來說，將是徒勞無功的。<ref name="zdnet-2">{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.zdnet.com/security/?p=1251|title=Blackmail ransomware returns with 1024-bit encryption key|accessdate=2009-05-03|date=2008-06-06|last=Naraine|first=Ryan|publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]]|archive-date=2008-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080803000014/http://blogs.zdnet.com/security/?p=1251|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="securityfocus">{{Cite web|url=http://www.securityfocus.com/news/11523|title=Ransomware resisting crypto cracking efforts|accessdate=2009-04-18|date=2008-06-13|last=Lemos|first=Robert|publisher=[[SecurityFocus|SecurityFocus]]|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303194706/http://www.securityfocus.com/news/11523|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="washingtonpost">{{Cite web|url=http://voices.washingtonpost.com/securityfix/2008/06/ransomware_encrypts_victim_fil.html|title=Ransomware Encrypts Victim Files with 1,024-Bit Key|accessdate=2009-04-16|date=2008-06-09|last=Krebs|first=Brian|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|archive-date=2012-05-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120531075611/http://voices.washingtonpost.com/securityfix/2008/06/ransomware_encrypts_victim_fil.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="kapersky">{{Cite web|url=http://www.kaspersky.com/news?id=207575650|title=Kaspersky Lab reports a new and dangerous blackmailing virus|accessdate=2008-06-11|date=2008-06-05|publisher=[[Kaspersky_Lab|Kaspersky Lab]]|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402173026/http://www.kaspersky.com/news?id=207575650|dead-url=no}}</ref>

加密勒索軟體隨著2013年尾開始出現行蹤的[[CryptoLocker|CryptoLocker]]又開始了新一波的活躍期，該病毒最大的差異在於利用新時代的[[比特币|比特幣]]進行勒索。2013年12月，''ZDNet''估計該病毒單單在該月（12月）15日至18日間，就利用[[比特币|比特幣]]從受害者身上汲取了2700萬美元的鉅額。<ref name="zdnet-bitcoinprice">{{Cite news|url=http://www.zdnet.com/cryptolockers-crimewave-a-trail-of-millions-in-laundered-bitcoin-7000024579/|title=CryptoLocker's crimewave: A trail of millions in laundered Bitcoin|date=2013-12-22|publisher=[[ZDNet|ZDNet]]|accessdate=2013-12-23|author=[[Violet_Blue|Violet Blue]]|archive-date=2013-12-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223011159/http://www.zdnet.com/cryptolockers-crimewave-a-trail-of-millions-in-laundered-bitcoin-7000024579/|dead-url=no}}</ref>CryptoLocker的手法在緊接著的幾個月內被多種病毒所效仿，包括CryptoLocker 2.0（被認為和原始的CryptoLocker無關）、CryptoDefense（值得注意的是，該病毒的初始版本包含了一個嚴重的設計缺陷，將私鑰儲存在[[Special_Folders|使用者能找到的位置]]，因為其使用Windows的內建加密API進行行動。）<ref name="computerworld-cryptodefense"/><ref name="pcworld-torrentlocker">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2685432/encryption-goof-fixed-in-torrentlocker-filelocking-malware.html|title=Encryption goof fixed in TorrentLocker file-locking malware|accessdate=2014-10-15|website=PC World|archive-date=2016-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506175524/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2685432/encryption-goof-fixed-in-torrentlocker-filelocking-malware.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="eset-cl2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.welivesecurity.com/2013/12/19/cryptolocker-2-0-new-version-or-copycat/|title=Cryptolocker 2.0 – new version, or copycat?|accessdate=2014-01-18|work=WeLiveSecurity|publisher=ESET|archive-date=2016-11-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122005648/http://www.welivesecurity.com/2013/12/19/cryptolocker-2-0-new-version-or-copycat/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="tm-newcl">{{Cite web|url=http://blog.trendmicro.com/trendlabs-security-intelligence/new-cryptolocker-spreads-via-removable-drives/|title=New CryptoLocker Spreads via Removable Drives|accessdate=2014-01-18|publisher=Trend Micro|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104095631/http://blog.trendmicro.com/trendlabs-security-intelligence/new-cryptolocker-spreads-via-removable-drives/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及2014年8月一個專門針對[[群暉科技|群暉科技]]（Synology）生產的[[網路附加儲存|網路附加儲存]]（NAS）設備進行攻擊的病毒。<ref name="extech-synologycrypto">{{Cite news|url=http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/187518-synology-nas-devices-targeted-by-hackers-demand-bitcoin-ransom-to-decrypt-files|title=Synology NAS devices targeted by hackers, demand Bitcoin ransom to decrypt files|work=ExtremeTech|publisher=Ziff Davis Media|accessdate=2014-08-18|archive-date=2014-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140819084648/http://www.extremetech.com/extreme/187518-synology-nas-devices-targeted-by-hackers-demand-bitcoin-ransom-to-decrypt-files|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在2014年尾，High-Tech Bridge資安公司甚至發現了將整個伺服器上網站都加密的RansomeWeb病毒。<ref name="forbesRansomWeb">{{Cite web|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/thomasbrewster/2015/01/28/ransomweb-50000-dollar-extortion/|title=RansomWeb: Crooks Start Encrypting Websites And Demanding Thousands Of Dollars From Businesses|accessdate=2016-01-12|last1=Fox-Brewster|first1=Thomas|website=Forbes.com}}</ref>

在2015年，刊載了一份詳盡的報告，列舉出不同的勒索軟體所使用的加密技術、弱點，及可能的防範措施等。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blog.checkpoint.com/2015/08/17/what-you-can-and-cant-do-against-ransomware/#comment-4052|title=What You Can (and Can't) Do Against Ransomware|accessdate=2016-03-14|author=Ben Herzog|date=2015-08-17|publisher=Checkpoint Technologies}}</ref>

2017年5月，勒索软件[[WannaCry|WannaCry]]大规模感染了包括[[西班牙電信|西班牙電信]]在内的许多西班牙公司、英国[[國民保健署_(英國)|國民保健署]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/society/2017/may/12/global-cyber-attack-nhs-trusts-malware|title=The NHS trusts hit by malware – full list|last=Marsh|first=Sarah|date=2017-05-12|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2017-05-13|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2017-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515202748/https://www.theguardian.com/society/2017/may/12/global-cyber-attack-nhs-trusts-malware|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[聯邦快遞|聯邦快遞]]和[[德国铁路|德国铁路股份公司]]。据报道，至少有99个国家的其他目标在同一时间遭到WanaCrypt0r 2.0的攻击。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://digital.nhs.uk/article/1491/Statement-on-reported-NHS-cyber-attack|title=Statement on reported NHS cyber attack|accessdate=2017-05-13|work=digital.nhs.uk|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519110600/https://digital.nhs.uk/article/1491/Statement-on-reported-NHS-cyber-attack|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/may/12/nhs-ransomware-cyber-attack-what-is-wanacrypt0r-20|title=What is 'WanaCrypt0r 2.0' ransomware and why is it attacking the NHS?|last=Hern|first=Alex|date=2017-05-12|last2=Gibbs|first2=Samuel|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2017-05-13|language=en-GB|issn=0261-3077|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512164110/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/may/12/nhs-ransomware-cyber-attack-what-is-wanacrypt0r-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBC news">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-39899646|title=NHS cyber-attack: GPs and hospitals hit by ransomware|date=2017-05-13|newspaper=BBC News|accessdate=2017-05-13|language=en-GB|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512145026/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/health-39899646|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name = "CNN WannaCry">{{Cite web|url=http://money.cnn.com/2017/05/12/technology/ransomware-attack-nsa-microsoft/index.html|title=Massive ransomware attack hits 99 countries|accessdate=2017-05-13|date=2017-05-12|last=Larson|first=Selena|work=CNNMoney|archive-date=2017-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170521054638/http://money.cnn.com/2017/05/12/technology/ransomware-attack-nsa-microsoft/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[俄罗斯联邦内务部|俄罗斯联邦内务部]]、[[俄羅斯聯邦緊急情況部|俄羅斯聯邦緊急情況部]]和俄罗斯电信公司MegaFon共有超过1000台计算机受到感染。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.rt.com/news/388153-thousands-ransomeware-attacks-worldwide/|title=Ransomware virus plagues 75k computers across 99 countries|newspaper=RT International|accessdate=2017-05-13|language=en-US}}</ref>[[中国教育网|中国教育网]]相连的中国大陆高校也出现大规模的感染<ref>{{cite web|title=安天发布措施紧急应对新型勒索软件“wannacry”|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/it/2017-05-13/doc-ifyfeivp5658790.shtml|website=新浪科技|accessdate=2017-05-13}}</ref>，感染甚至波及到了[[公安机关|公安机关]]使用的[[内网|内网]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/612213.htm|title=勒索病毒国内蔓延 多地出入境系统受影响瘫痪_警告!_cnBeta.COM|accessdate=2017-05-13|last=cnBeta|work=cnbeta|language=zh-CN}}</ref>，使得[[河南省|河南省]][[洛阳市|洛阳市]]的公安系统遭到破坏<ref>{{cite web|title=勒索病毒来袭 洛阳市这些单位办理业务受影响|url=http://henan.163.com/17/0515/13/CKFTVGMC04398DOB.html|website=网易新闻|accessdate=2017-05-15}}{{Dead link|date=2019年12月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。[[国家互联网应急中心|国家互联网应急中心]]亦发布通报<ref>{{cite web|title=国家互联网应急中心发布勒索软件情况通报|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/i/2017-05-13/doc-ifyfeius7896234.shtml|website=新浪科技|accessdate=2017-05-13|date=2017-05-13}}</ref>。

2020年12月23日，美国各级政府部门、北约、英国政府、欧洲议会、微软等至少200个政府单位、组织或公司[[2020年美国联邦政府数据泄露事件|遭遇数据泄露]]，影响范围甚广<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html|title=Scope of Russian Hack Becomes Clear: Multiple U.S. Agencies Were Hit|first=David E.|author=Sanger|first2=Nicole|author2=Perlroth|first3=Eric|last3=Schmitt|date=December 15, 2020|work=The New York Times|accessdate=December 15, 2020|archivedate=December 18, 2020|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218062201/https://www.nytimes.com/2020/12/14/us/politics/russia-hack-nsa-homeland-security-pentagon.html}}</ref>。

2021年5月7日，起源于美国[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]][[休斯敦|休斯敦]]、主要负责向[[美国东南部|美国东南部]]运输[[重油|重油]]的[[管道运输|石油管道]]系统[[殖民管道|殖民管道]]遭遇[[DarkSide|DarkSide]]发动的勒索软件[[殖民管道網絡攻擊|网络攻击]]，影响负责管理管道的计算机系统，导致服务地区出现燃油短缺情况<ref>{{Cite web|last=Helmore|first=Edward|date=2021-05-10|title=FBI confirms DarkSide hacking group behind US pipeline shutdown|url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/may/10/colonial-pipeline-shutdown-us-darkside-message|dead-url=no|access-date=2021-05-10|website=The Guardian|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512115806/https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/may/10/colonial-pipeline-shutdown-us-darkside-message}}</ref>。

=== 非加密性勒索軟體 ===
在2010年8月，俄羅斯當局逮捕了十名與WinLock木馬病毒有關聯的嫌犯。WinLock病毒並不像前面所提到的Gpcode一樣對電腦加密，相反的，WinLock顯示色情圖片遮擋使用者的電腦螢幕，並提示受害者利用大約10美元的[[簡訊|簡訊]]付費以接收解鎖的密碼。這個病毒襲擊了俄羅斯及鄰近國家的許多人，並被報導指出，攻擊者賺取了超過一千六百萬美元的收入。<ref name="pcw-russia"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/09/01/ransomware_trojan_suspects_cuffed/|title=Russian cops cuff 10 ransomware Trojan suspects|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Leyden|first=John|publisher=The Register|archive-date=2017-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222170927/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2010/09/01/ransomware_trojan_suspects_cuffed/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2011年，一個勒索軟體假藉Windows產品啟用的名義行騙，提示受害者的Windows因為是詐騙的受害者（''victim of fraud''），所以必須重新啟用。就像真正的產品啟用一樣，病毒也提供了線上啟動的選項，卻顯示成無法使用，並要求受害者撥打六支[[國際電話|國際電話]]的其中一隻，並且輸入六位數密碼。雖然病毒宣稱該電話號碼為免費撥打，電話卻實際上會被轉接到高費率的國家，再刻意將該通話置於保留（''on hold''），藉此讓受害者付出高額的國際[[長途電話|長途電話]]費用。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="114"></span><ref name="cw-ranactivate"/>

2013年，一款基於Stamp.EK攻擊套件的病毒浮上檯面。該病毒散發訊息在各個[[SourceForge|SourceForge]]和[[GitHub|GitHub]]專案頁面中，並宣稱提供名人的假造裸照。<ref name="tnw-fakenudepics">{{Cite web|url=http://thenextweb.com/insider/2013/02/07/criminals-push-ransomware-hosted-on-github-and-sourceforge-pages-by-spamming-fake-nude-pics-of-celebrities/|title=Criminals push ransomware hosted on GitHub and SourceForge pages by spamming ‘fake nude pics’ of celebrities|accessdate=2013-07-17|work=TheNextWeb|archive-date=2017-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216195701/https://thenextweb.com/insider/2013/02/07/criminals-push-ransomware-hosted-on-github-and-sourceforge-pages-by-spamming-fake-nude-pics-of-celebrities/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2013年7月，一個針對[[OS_X|OS X]]的勒索軟體出現。該病毒會顯示一個網頁，宣稱受害者被發現下載色情媒體。不像Windows的病毒一樣對整個系統上鎖，該病毒只能利用[[点击劫持|點擊劫持]]來混淆受害者的視聽，試圖不讓受害者用正常方式關閉該頁面。<ref name="tnw-osxransom">{{Cite web|url=http://thenextweb.com/apple/2013/07/16/new-os-x-malware-holds-macs-for-ransom-demands-300-fine-to-the-fbi-for-viewing-or-distributing-porn/|title=New OS X malware holds Macs for ransom, demands $300 fine to the FBI for ‘viewing or distributing’ porn|accessdate=2013-07-17|work=TheNextWeb|archive-date=2017-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170103012931/http://thenextweb.com/apple/2013/07/16/new-os-x-malware-holds-macs-for-ransom-demands-300-fine-to-the-fbi-for-viewing-or-distributing-porn//|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年7月，一名來自[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]的21歲男子中了勒索軟體，卻在巧合之下，因為自己的電腦確實儲存了和他聊天過的未成年少女的裸照，而病毒顯示FBI查獲兒童色情媒體的警告，向警方自首。<ref name="ars-cpvirginia">{{Cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2013/07/man-gets-ransomware-porn-pop-up-turns-self-in-on-child-porn-charges/|title=Man gets ransomware porn pop-up, goes to cops, gets arrested on child porn charges|accessdate=2013-07-31|work=Ars Technica|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109092847/http://arstechnica.com/tech-policy/2013/07/man-gets-ransomware-porn-pop-up-turns-self-in-on-child-porn-charges/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
2016年1月，也發現了威脅要將受害者的瀏覽紀錄公開的勒索軟體。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2016/01/29/android_ransomware/|title=Two-thirds of Android users vulnerable to web history sniff ransomware|date=2016-01-28|accessdate=2016-02-01|last1=Leyden|first1=John}}</ref>

== 案例 ==

=== Reveton ===
2012年，一款叫做Reveton的勒索軟體開始廣布。該病毒基於Citadel木馬病毒，而病毒的有效數據會顯示假造成來自執法機關的訊息（因此，此類病毒又被稱為''police Trojan''或''cop Trojan''）。該病毒會宣稱執法機關查獲該電腦有非法活動，例如下載[[盗版|盜版軟體]]或是[[兒童色情|兒童色情媒體]]<ref name="reg-reve">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/04/05/police_themed_ransomware/|title=Fake cop Trojan 'detects offensive materials' on PCs, demands money|accessdate=2012-08-15|publisher=The Register|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109035409/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2012/04/05/police_themed_ransomware/|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，並且提示受害者使用Ukash 或Paysafecard等匿名電子貨幣進行繳納。為了更進一步取信於被害人，該警訊也會同時列出受害者的[[IP地址|IP位址]]，某些版本甚至會顯示受害者[[網路攝影機|網路攝影機]]的畫面。<ref name="tw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|title=Ransom Trojans spreading beyond Russian heartland|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702211354/http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="iw-fbi">{{Cite web|url=http://www.informationweek.com/security/attacks/reveton-malware-freezes-pcs-demands-paym/240005598|title=Reveton Malware Freezes PCs, Demands Payment|accessdate=2012-08-16|publisher=InformationWeek|archive-date=2013-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514122409/http://www.informationweek.com/security/attacks/reveton-malware-freezes-pcs-demands-paym/240005598|dead-url=no}}</ref>

Reveton在2012年開始在歐洲各國間活動。<ref name="tw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|title=Ransom Trojans spreading beyond Russian heartland|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702211354/http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>變種則有各式各樣的在地化版本，搭配受害者語言與當地執法機關的圖示。例如在[[英國|英國]]的變種就會顯示成[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]、著作權集體管理團體 PRS for Music（搭配受害者下載盜版音樂的警告）、PeCU等。<ref name="tw-pecu">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3373656/police-issue-alert-after-ransom-trojan-infects-1100-pcs/|title=Police alert after ransom Trojan locks up 1,100 PCs|accessdate=2012-08-16|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702202942/http://news.techworld.com/security/3373656/police-issue-alert-after-ransom-trojan-infects-1100-pcs/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref> 倫敦警察廳曾公開澄清，執法單位絕對不會像病毒一樣，將使用者的電腦以調查名義鎖上。<ref name="tw-russia">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|title=Ransom Trojans spreading beyond Russian heartland|accessdate=2012-03-10|last=Dunn|first=John E.|publisher=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702211354/http://news.techworld.com/security/3343528/ransom-trojans-spreading-beyond-russian-heartland/|archive-date=2014-07-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="hsfi-ransom">{{Cite web|url=http://www.hs.fi/english/article/Police+warn+of+extortion+messages+sent+in+their+name/1329103586716|title=Police warn of extortion messages sent in their name|accessdate=2012-03-09|publisher=[[Helsingin_Sanomat|Helsingin Sanomat]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314102017/http://www.hs.fi/english/article/Police+warn+of+extortion+messages+sent+in+their+name/1329103586716|archivedate=2012-03-14}}</ref>

2012年5月，[[趨勢科技|趨勢科技]]研究員發現[[美國|美國]]及[[加拿大|加拿大]]的版本，代表病毒開發者可能本來有意攻擊北美地區。<ref name="pcw-canusa">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/businesscenter/article/255303/policethemed_ransomware_starts_targeting_us_and_canadian_users.html|title=Police-themed Ransomware Starts Targeting US and Canadian Users|accessdate=2012-05-11|last=Constantian|first=Lucian|publisher=PC World}}</ref> 2012年8月，Reveton的新變種開始在美國流竄，要求受害者用MoneyPak卡向FBI繳納200美元的罰鍰。<ref name="FBI"/><ref name="IC3"/><ref name="iw-fbi"/> 2013年2月，一個俄羅斯公民在[[杜拜|杜拜]]遭西班牙當局逮捕，因為被發現他所屬的犯罪組織曾使用過Reveton；十名共犯則以[[洗錢|洗錢]]罪名逮捕。<ref name="tw-revetonarrest">{{Cite web|url=http://news.techworld.com/security/3426085/reveton-police-ransom-malware-gang-head-arrested-in-dubai/|title=Reveton 'police ransom' malware gang head arrested in Dubai|accessdate=2014-10-18|website=TechWorld|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141214021849/http://news.techworld.com/security/3426085/reveton-police-ransom-malware-gang-head-arrested-in-dubai/|archive-date=2014-12-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年8月，Avast Software回報發現新變種，攜帶竊取密碼的軟體作為實體數據之一。<ref name="pcw-revetonupgrade">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2466980/reveton-ransomware-upgraded-with-powerful-password-stealer.html|title='Reveton' ransomware upgraded with powerful password stealer|accessdate=2014-10-18|website=PC World|archive-date=2016-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402050626/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2466980/reveton-ransomware-upgraded-with-powerful-password-stealer.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== CryptoLocker ===
2013年9月，加密性勒索軟體以[[CryptoLocker|CryptoLocker]]之姿重出江湖。該病毒使用2048位元的RSA加密金鑰，並將其回傳至主控病毒行動的伺服器。關於加密檔案，該病毒使用白名單以只對特定的[[文件扩展名|副檔名]]加密。CryptoLocker威脅受害者，若不以[[比特币|比特币]]或付費卡在三天內繳款，就會將所有加密檔案刪除。由於其使用了極大長度的金鑰，被其加密的檔案一般是認為無法復原的。<ref name="ars-cryptolocker"/><ref name="geek-cryptolocker">{{Cite web|url=http://www.geek.com/apps/disk-encryptiing-cryptolocker-malware-demands-300-to-decrypt-your-files-1570402/|title=Disk encrypting Cryptolocker malware demands $300 to decrypt your files|accessdate=2013-09-12|work=Geek.com|archive-date=2016-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104045318/http://www.geek.com/apps/disk-encryptiing-cryptolocker-malware-demands-300-to-decrypt-your-files-1570402/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="guardian-cryptolocker">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/oct/19/cryptolocker-attacks-computer-ransomeware|title=CryptoLocker attacks that hold your computer to ransom|accessdate=2013-10-23|work=The Guardian|archive-date=2013-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131118225033/http://www.theguardian.com/money/2013/oct/19/cryptolocker-attacks-computer-ransomeware|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="sophos-cryptolocker">{{Cite web|url=http://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2013/10/12/destructive-malware-cryptolocker-on-the-loose/|title=Destructive malware "CryptoLocker" on the loose - here's what to do|accessdate=2013-10-23|work=Naked Security|publisher=Sophos|archive-date=2017-05-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170508022456/https://nakedsecurity.sophos.com/2013/10/12/destructive-malware-cryptolocker-on-the-loose/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 儘管付款期限已過，解密的金鑰仍能利用其提供的線上工具取得，但是價格會增加為10[[BTC|BTC]]，相當於2300美元（2013年11月匯率）。<ref name="nw-cryptolockersecondchance">{{Cite web|url=http://www.networkworld.com/community/node/84174|title=CryptoLocker crooks charge 10 Bitcoins for second-chance decryption service|accessdate=2013-11-05|work=NetworkWorld|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105175934/http://www.networkworld.com/community/node/84174|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pcw-moremoney">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2060640/cryptolocker-creators-try-to-extort-even-more-money-from-victims-with-new-service.html|title=CryptoLocker creators try to extort even more money from victims with new service|accessdate=2013-11-05|work=PC World|archive-date=2017-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430230656/http://pcworld.com/article/2060640/cryptolocker-creators-try-to-extort-even-more-money-from-victims-with-new-service.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[美國司法部|美國司法部]]在2014年6月2日宣布，CryptoLocker在Gameover ZeuS[[殭屍網絡|殭屍網絡]]遭到執法機關關閉後被分離出來。司法部也提起了對俄國駭客Evgeniy Bogachev的[[公訴|公訴]]，因為其對該殭屍網路運作的涉入。<ref name="cw-whambam">{{Cite news|url=http://blogs.computerworld.com/cybercrime-and-hacking/23980/wham-bam-global-operation-tovar-whacks-cryptolocker-ransomware-gameover-zeus-botnet|title=Wham bam: Global Operation Tovar whacks CryptoLocker ransomware & GameOver Zeus botnet|work=Computerworld|accessdate=2014-08-18|agency=IDG|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140703092912/http://blogs.computerworld.com/cybercrime-and-hacking/23980/wham-bam-global-operation-tovar-whacks-cryptolocker-ransomware-gameover-zeus-botnet|archivedate=2014-07-03}}</ref><ref name="doj-takedown">{{Cite news|url=http://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/2014/June/14-crm-584.html|title=U.S. Leads Multi-National Action Against "Gameover Zeus" Botnet and "Cryptolocker" Ransomware, Charges Botnet Administrator|work=Justice.gov|accessdate=2014-08-18|agency=U.S. Department of Justice|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903075329/http://www.justice.gov/opa/pr/2014/June/14-crm-584.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 據估計，在該病毒遭關閉前，已經獲得了至少三百萬美元的收入。<ref name="cl-takedown"/>

=== CryptoLocker.F 與 TorrentLocker ===
2014年9月，新一波針對[[澳洲|澳洲]]的勒索攻擊開始，以''CryptoWall''及''CryptoLocker''（連同CryptoLocker 2.0，不和原始CryptoLocker有關）。該病毒透過假造的電子郵件散布，宣稱受害者有投遞失敗的[[澳大利亞郵政|澳大利亞郵政]]包裹。為了避開安全軟體的掃瞄，該變種會先提示使用者輸入[[验证码|CAPTCHA驗證碼]]來誘使受害者下載病毒數據。[[赛门铁克|赛门铁克]]確認了該變種，命名為''CryptoLocker.F''。<ref name="symantec-aus">{{Cite web|url=http://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/australians-increasingly-hit-global-tide-cryptomalware|title=Australians increasingly hit by global tide of cryptomalware|accessdate=2014-10-15|publisher=Symantec|archive-date=2016-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329043821/http://www.symantec.com/connect/blogs/australians-increasingly-hit-global-tide-cryptomalware|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="smh-lockup">{{Cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/it-pro/security-it/hackers-lock-up-thousands-of-australian-computers-demand-ransom-20140917-10hyyh.html|title=Hackers lock up thousands of Australian computers, demand ransom|date=2014-09-17|work=Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2014-10-15|last1=Grubb|first1=Ben|archive-date=2014-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141020040609/http://www.smh.com.au/it-pro/security-it/hackers-lock-up-thousands-of-australian-computers-demand-ransom-20140917-10hyyh.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 其中的一個受害者是[[澳大利亚广播公司|澳洲廣播公司]]，而其現場轉播的[[新聞頻道|新聞頻道]]ABC News 24被迫中斷半小時並轉至[[墨尔本|墨尔本]]攝影棚錄影，因為[[悉尼|雪梨]]的攝影棚被該病毒攻擊了。<ref name="arn-cryptolockerf">{{Cite news|url=http://www.arnnet.com.au/article/556598/australia-specifically-targeted-by-cryptolocker-symantec/|title=Australia specifically targeted by Cryptolocker: Symantec|date=2014-10-03|work=ARNnet|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007191221/http://www.arnnet.com.au/article/556598/australia-specifically-targeted-by-cryptolocker-symantec/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="smh-cryptowall">{{Cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/consumer-security/scammers-use-australia-post-to-mask-email-attacks-20141015-10ru0s.html|title=Scammers use Australia Post to mask email attacks|date=2014-10-15|work=Sydney Morning Herald|accessdate=2014-10-15|archive-date=2014-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141016045825/http://www.smh.com.au/digital-life/consumer-security/scammers-use-australia-post-to-mask-email-attacks-20141015-10ru0s.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cso-abcnews24">{{Cite web|url=http://www.csoonline.com/article/2692614/malware-cybercrime/ransomware-attack-knocks-tv-station-off-air.html|title=Ransomware attack knocks TV station off air|accessdate=2014-10-15|website=CSO|archive-date=2016-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161012223059/http://www.csoonline.com/article/2692614/malware-cybercrime/ransomware-attack-knocks-tv-station-off-air.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

另一個搭上順風車的病毒TorrentLocker，最初含有與CryptoDefense類似的缺陷。該病毒對每台受感染的電腦都使用相同的[[密钥流|密鑰流]]，導致安全單位能利用此弱點解開加密的檔案。該缺陷在後來的版本中被修正了。<ref name="pcworld-torrentlocker"/> 在2014年尾，估計光是澳洲就有超過9000名受害者受TorrentLocker所害，僅次於[[土耳其|土耳其]]的11,700名。<ref name="cso-torrentlocker">{{Cite web|url=http://www.cso.com.au/article/562658/over-9-000-pcs-australia-infected-by-torrentlocker-ransomware/|title=Over 9,000 (Vegeta - "OVER 9000!!!!!!!") PCs in Australia infected by TorrentLocker ransomware|accessdate=2014-12-18|website=CSO.com.au|archive-date=2016-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161111070637/http://www.cso.com.au/article/562658/over-9-000-pcs-australia-infected-by-torrentlocker-ransomware/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== CryptoWall ===
另一個針對Windows的重大病毒CryptoWall在2014年出現。CryptoWall隨著Zedo廣告網的[[惡意廣告|惡意廣告]]散布。在2014年9月，其針對數個主要網站進行了攻擊，將受害者導向至獨立網站，利用瀏覽器漏洞傳輸病毒。一名Barracuda Networks研究員發現該病毒帶有[[數位簽章|數位簽章]]，以取信於安全軟體。<ref name="pcw-signedcryptowall">{{Cite web|url=http://www.pcworld.com/article/2688992/malvertising-campaign-delivers-digitally-signed-cryptowall-ransomware.html|title=Malvertising campaign delivers digitally signed CryptoWall ransomware|accessdate=2015-06-25|website=PC World|archive-date=2016-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160719061434/http://www.pcworld.com/article/2688992/malvertising-campaign-delivers-digitally-signed-cryptowall-ransomware.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 
CryptoWall 3.0以[[JavaScript|JavaScript]]寫成，作為電子郵件的附加檔案。該腳本會下載偽裝成[[JPEG|JPG]]圖檔的可執行檔。為了更進一步避開偵測，該病毒會建立複製的[[檔案總管|explorer.exe]]及[[svchost.exe|svchost.exe]]與其伺服器溝通。建立加密檔案時，該病毒也會同時刪除系統還原的備份檔案，並且安裝[[間諜軟體|間諜軟體]]，竊取受害者的密碼與[[比特币|比特幣錢包]]。<ref name="tm-cw3">{{Cite web|url=http://blog.trendmicro.com/trendlabs-security-intelligence/cryptowall-3-0-ransomware-partners-with-fareit-spyware/|title=CryptoWall 3.0 Ransomware Partners With FAREIT Spyware|accessdate=2015-06-25|publisher=Trend Micro|archive-date=2016-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018224354/http://blog.trendmicro.com/trendlabs-security-intelligence/cryptowall-3-0-ransomware-partners-with-fareit-spyware/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

聯邦調查局表示，在2015年6月有上千名的受害者向網路犯罪回報中心回報了CryptoWall的感染，估計損失至少一千八百萬美元。<ref name="ars-fbicryptowall"/>

在最新的4.0版本中，CryptoWall改進了其程式碼以避免防毒軟體的偵測，並且除了檔案內容外，也一併加密檔案名稱。<ref name="heimdal">{{Cite web|url=https://heimdalsecurity.com/blog/security-alert-cryptowall-4-0-new-enhanced-and-more-difficult-to-detect/|title=Security Alert: CryptoWall 4.0 – new, enhanced and more difficult to detect|accessdate=2016-01-05|author=Andra Zaharia|date=2015-11-05|website=HEIMDAL|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110225641/https://heimdalsecurity.com/blog/security-alert-cryptowall-4-0-new-enhanced-and-more-difficult-to-detect/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== KeRanger ===
KeRanger在2016年3月出現，是第一個在[[OS_X|OS X]]作業系統上運作的勒索軟體。該病毒加密受害者的個人檔案，並且要求1[[BTC|BTC]]的贖金以解密檔案。該病毒將.DMG可執行檔偽裝成[[RTF|RTF]]檔案。該病毒會潛伏三日，接著開始加密檔案，再附上一個寫入解密教學的文字檔案。該病毒也使用2048位元的RSA公鑰加密檔案。後續研究表明，該病毒其實是Linux.Encoder.1為[[OS_X|OS X]]系統而重寫的。

=== RSA4096 ===
RSA4096是目前加密性勒索軟體的最新世代。最初出現於2015年，該病毒使用[[公开密钥加密|公鑰加密]]，付款則要求受害者利用[[比特币|比特幣]]向暗網內的代理人購買，卻不保證在付款後能取回私鑰。該病毒有數種變種，大部分都尚未找到解決辦法。某些變種會將檔案的副檔名改變。唯一從攻擊中復原的方法，除了付費購買私鑰以外，只有從外部裝置復原受感染的檔案一途。 由於比特幣匯率近年的大幅上升，贖金的價格也相對的上升了。在2016年4月，該價格大約為三十萬英鎊。

''' Manamecrypt (CryptoHost)'''<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/cryptohost-decrypted-locks-files-in-a-password-protected-rar-file/|title=CryptoHost Decrypted: Locks files in a password protected RAR File|language=en-us|website=BleepingComputer|access-date=2016-04-20}}</ref>

該病毒宣稱加密受害者的檔案，並且要求1/3BTC（大約140美元）來解密檔案。事實上，該病毒卻不將檔案加密，而是將檔案移動進入密碼保護的[[RAR|RAR]]壓縮檔。 不過壓縮檔的密碼很容易找到，使得受害者有方法能取回受感染的檔案。 

CryptoHost將受害者的檔案移至''C:\Users\使用者名稱\AppData\Roaming''的一個RAR壓縮檔內。 檔案名稱為41個字元，且沒有副檔名。<span class="cx-segment" data-segmentid="305"></span>

CryptoHost目前綑綁在竄改的[[μTorrent|μTorrent]]安裝程式內，將自身的cryptohost.exe解壓縮進入''%AppData%''後執行病毒。

=== Mischa ===
Mischa是一款勒索軟體，並且和Petya勒索軟體有明顯的關聯。 該病毒會將加密的檔案改為特定的副檔名，如.3P7m、''.arpT''、.''eQTz''、''.3RNu''等。遭受感染的受害者電腦會在瀏覽器內顯示出威脅訊息，聲稱電腦已經遭到「軍規級加密」。該病毒也利用[[Tor|Tor]]瀏覽器和暗網（[[Tor|Tor]]隐藏服务）要求比特幣贖金，價值通常介於20美元至1000美元間。

=== WannaCrypt ===
[[WannaCrypt|WannaCrypt]]是利用Windows系統漏洞進行侵入的一款勒索病毒，在2017年5月12日後全球超过230,000台计算机皆遭此病毒侵害，此病毒要求支付价值等同于300美元的比特幣才可解密所有遭加密文件。受害者電腦大多數皆裝載Windows 7系統，微軟也針對此漏洞進行更新。<ref name = "CNN WannaCrypt"/>

=== Petya ===
{{main|Petya}}
Petya于2016年3月首次出现，不像其他加密勒索软件，该恶意软件旨在感染[[主引导记录|主引导记录]]，安装有效负载，受感染的系统下次引导时便加密[[NTFS|NTFS]]文件系统文件表，完全阻止系统引导进Windows，直至支付赎金。[[Check_Point|Check Point]]报告指出，尽管该软件被认为是勒索软件设计上的创新性进展，但和在相同时间范围内话语的其他软件相比，感染率相对较低<ref name="nw-petyadouble">{{Cite news|url=http://www.networkworld.com/article/3069990/petya-ransomware-is-now-double-the-trouble.html|title=Petya ransomware is now double the trouble|last=Constantin|first=Lucian|work=NetworkWorld|access-date=2017-06-27|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731151832/http://www.networkworld.com/article/3069990/petya-ransomware-is-now-double-the-trouble.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年6月27日，Petya重大修改版本被用来反动主要针对乌克兰的全球性网络攻击。经修改的版本和WannaCry同样使用永恒之蓝漏洞传播。由于设计变更，即使支付赎金系统也不会真正解锁，故安全分析师猜测这次袭击不是为了获取非法利益，仅仅是搞破坏<ref name="ars-wiper">{{Cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/security/2017/06/petya-outbreak-was-a-chaos-sowing-wiper-not-profit-seeking-ransomware/|title=Tuesday’s massive ransomware outbreak was, in fact, something much worse|language=en-us|access-date=2017-06-28|work=Ars Technica|archive-date=2017-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170717073820/https://arstechnica.com/security/2017/06/petya-outbreak-was-a-chaos-sowing-wiper-not-profit-seeking-ransomware/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="BBCPMdc">{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-40442578|title=Cyber-attack was about data and not money, say experts|last=|first=|date=2017-06-29|work=BBC News|access-date=2017-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190805135949/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-40442578|archive-date=2019-08-05|dead-url=no|language=en-GB}}</ref>。

=== Bad Rabbit ===
2017年10月24日，俄罗斯和乌克兰有用户报告了新型勒索软件“Bad Rabbit”。类似于WannaCry和Petya的模式，Bad Rabbit加密了用户的文件表后，要求支付比特币解锁。[[ESET|ESET]]认为，该勒索软件伪装成[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]更新发布<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-41740768 | title = 'Bad Rabbit' ransomware strikes Ukraine and Russia | date = 2017-10-24 | accessdate = 2017-10-24 | work = [[BBC|BBC]] }}</ref>。受影响的机构包括[[国际文传电讯社|国际文传电讯社]]、[[敖德萨国际机场|敖德萨国际机场]]、[[基辅地铁|基辅地铁]]和乌克兰基础设施部<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2017/oct/25/bad-rabbit-game-of-thrones-ransomware-europe-notpetya-bitcoin-decryption-key|title=Bad Rabbit: Game of Thrones-referencing ransomware hits Europe|first=Alex|last=Hern|date=2017-10-25|accessdate=2017-10-25|website=Theguardian.com}}</ref>。由于利用网络结构进行传播，软件也流入到别国，如土耳其、德国、波兰、日本、韩国和美国<ref name="cnn badrabbit"/>。专家认为此番袭击和乌克兰的Petya袭击有关，尽管罪魁祸首的唯一标识是将《[[权力的游戏_(电视剧)|权力的游戏]]》系列角色的名字嵌入代码<ref name="cnn badrabbit"/>。

安全专家发现，软件没有使用永恒之蓝漏洞，这种给运行旧版Windows的未被感染的机器接种疫苗的简单方法传播<ref>{{cite web | url = https://gizmodo.com/bad-rabbit-ransomware-strikes-russia-and-ukraine-1819814538 | title = 'Bad Rabbit' Ransomware Strikes Russia and Ukraine | first = Dell | last = Cameron | date = 2017-10-24 | accessdate = 2017-10-24 | work = [[Gizmodo|Gizmodo]] }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.zdnet.com/article/bad-rabbit-ransomware-a-new-variant-of-petya-is-spreading-warn-researchers/ | title = Bad Rabbit ransomware: A new variant of Petya is spreading, warn researchers | first = Danny | last = Palmer | date=  2017-10-24 | accessdate = 2017-10-24 | work = [[ZDNet|ZDNet]] }}</ref>。此外，一直用来传播假Flash更新已经离线，或是在勒索软件被发现后几天内删除了有问题的文件，从而有效阻止软件传播<ref name="cnn badrabbit">{{cite web | url = http://money.cnn.com/2017/10/24/technology/bad-rabbit-ransomware-attack/index.html | title = New ransomware attack hits Russia and spreads around globe |first = Selena | last = Larson | date = 2017-10-25 | accessdate = 2017-10-25 | work = [[CNN|CNN]] }}</ref>。

== 勒索軟體即服務（Ransomware as a service） ==
暗網中已有越來越多的人宣稱提供勒索軟體[[软件即服务|作為服務]]，例如現在已經失效的Tox<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://threatpost.com/author-behind-ransomware-tox-calls-it-quits-sells-platform/113151|title=Author Behind Ransomware Tox Calls it Quits, Sells Platform|date=2015-06-04|accessdate=2015-08-06|last1=Brook|first1=Chris|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180929000313/https://threatpost.com/author-behind-ransomware-tox-calls-it-quits-sells-platform/113151/|archive-date=2018-09-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>與Encryptor RaaS等。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://blog.fortinet.com/post/encryptor-raas-yet-another-new-ransomware-as-a-service-on-the-block|title=Encryptor RaaS: Yet another new Ransomware-as-a-Service on the Block|date=2015-07-29|accessdate=2015-08-06|last1=Dela Paz|first1=Roland|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516023120/http://blog.fortinet.com/post/encryptor-raas-yet-another-new-ransomware-as-a-service-on-the-block|archivedate=2016-05-16}}</ref>

== 反制 ==
就像其他形式的惡意軟體一樣，安全軟體不一定能偵測出勒索軟體的實體數據──尤其是加密用的軟體──直到開始加密或是完成加密了才被發現。對於[[零日攻擊|未知的病毒]]來說更是如此。<ref name="yumasun-cryptolocker">{{Cite news|url=http://www.yumasun.com/news/local/article_f38f14e8-4f50-11e3-8165-0019bb30f31a.html|title=Yuma Sun weathers malware attack|work=[[Yuma_Sun|Yuma Sun]]|accessdate=2014-08-18|archive-date=2017-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171008143617/http://www.yumasun.com/news/local/article_f38f14e8-4f50-11e3-8165-0019bb30f31a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 若攻擊尚在早期階段，加密檔案尚未成功，此時強制移除病毒實體數據就能避免對資料的進一步加密，例如拔除電源等物理性做法也是可以搶救回部分資料。<ref name="malwarebytes">{{Cite web|url=http://blog.malwarebytes.org/intelligence/2013/10/CryptoLocker-ransomware-what-you-need-to-know/|title=Cryptolocker Ransomware: What You Need To Know, last updated 06/02/2014|accessdate=2013-10-19|last=Cannell|first=Joshua|work=Malwarebytes Unpacked|archive-date=2016-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160314184323/https://blog.malwarebytes.org/intelligence/2013/10/CryptoLocker-ransomware-what-you-need-to-know/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="register">{{Cite web|url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/10/18/cryptolocker_ransmware|title=Fiendish CryptoLocker ransomware: Whatever you do, don't PAY|accessdate=2013-10-18|last=Leyden|first=Josh|work=The Register|archive-date=2016-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161110081144/http://www.theregister.co.uk/2013/10/18/cryptolocker_ransmware/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 安全專家建議了一些預防措施來應對勒索軟體，例如使用安全軟體或設定以避免已知的勒索軟體執行；保留與不與電腦連接的資料備份，尤其某些病毒會將仍與電腦連接的備份檔案一併加密。<ref name="ars-cryptolocker"/><ref name="securityweek131119"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.securityweek.com/cryptolocker-infections-rise-us-cert-issues-warning "Cryptolocker Infections on the Rise; US-CERT Issues Warning"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.securityweek.com/cryptolocker-infections-rise-us-cert-issues-warning |date=20160610183317 }}. </cite></ref>非加密性勒索軟體能被專家移除，或是利用現成的安全軟體刪除。

雖然勒索軟體的威脅無法被完全革除，使用IT業界所稱的多層次預防策略（defense-in-layers security strategy）卻稱得上是不錯的預防手段。多層次預防策略提倡同時部署多種獨立、領域互相重疊的安全措施以建立穩固的安全措施。各安全層被設計和其他安全層互補，使得威脅不易穿透重重防護。例如一個安全策略可能包含下列五層： <ref name="academia.edu">[https://www.academia.edu/24409160/5_Steps_to_Take_on_Ransomware_A_Defense-in-Layers_Approach Musa, S. (2016). 5 Steps to Take on Ransomware.]</ref>
* 全面性的、完備的安全政策
* 網路和郵件的內容過濾代理伺服器
* 限制級別存取
* 以密碼上鎖特定功能
* 不間斷的員工警覺性訓練

